[src:gtk4/glib-p01] E.g. the file size 3292528 bytes will be converted into the string “3.2 MB”.
[src:gtk4/glib-p01] The returned string is UTF-8, and may use a non-breaking space to separate the number and units, to ensure they aren’t separated when line wrapped.
